Full text bundled alongside this file as OFL.txt.

This subset retains only the glyphs needed by the test fixture's
multi-language tags (Latin extended, Cyrillic, Hiragana, Han, Hangul:
86 codepoints in total). It was produced with fonttools subset and is
not intended for any use other than reproducing the page-break-inside
ancestor-walk bug fixed in
PdfBoxAccessibilityHelper.ensureAncestorTree.
